358
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:09,280
[Then what about Shi Meng?]

359
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:12,280
Can you do that or not? Stop fidgeting.

360
00:19:12,280 --> 00:19:14,970
Quiet. Let me think in peace.

361
