Zuo Yao is the key.

379
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:11,920
If Fang Yan blossoms,

380
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:14,280
Zuo Yao will be won over
by my capabilities.

381
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:16,040
She would even beg me not to leave.

382
00:20:16,040 --> 00:20:17,320
But I'll reject her straight out.

383
00:20:17,320 --> 00:20:18,180
Do you know why?

384
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:19,560
Because only I, Hao Ying Jun, could
come up with...

385
00:20:19,560 --> 00:20:21,640
