00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:21,520
Fang Yan.

551
00:29:25,120 --> 00:29:27,780
The bed of a superstar feels totally different.

552
00:29:28,360 --> 00:29:29,490
Such great quality.

553
00:29:46,760 --> 00:29:47,920
So pretty.

554
00:29:57,640 --> 00:29:59,770
Why didn't aunt switch off the lights?

555
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:06,370
But she cleaned the place really good.

556
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:33,470
