I introduce myself to you.

564
00:31:21,840 --> 00:31:24,640
Don't worry, Shi Yi. I won't say
a word to your fans.

565
00:31:24,720 --> 00:31:27,100
That you have a birth mark on your...

566
00:31:28,770 --> 00:31:30,440
-It's you?
